text: Oleksiy Pinchuk (; born 17 February 1992 in Dnipropetrovsk, Ukraine) is a Ukrainian football midfielder who plays for Hirnyk-Sport Horishni Plavni. Pinchuk is a product of the FC Dnipro youth sportive school.
